{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 382.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And by the time we noticed these two monsters, they were shaved in these rags.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we suddenly yelled, ah, ah, Regina, Zippy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They're my sisters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So there were four of us, but a few minutes ago we were a big family of seven.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, through the window, somehow this archangel of a human being, my brother, managed to-- he was already shaved and he was given a striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he managed to climb through the window, taking a chance on being shot if they notice him, just so that he can give us one word of encouragement.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he took the four of us and he said, listen to me, listen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Eat everything they give you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If they give you shit, eat shit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we must survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We have to pay them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Not only pay them back, we have to create a better world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he disappeared through the window and I never saw him again until I was in America, in 1946, when he arrived in January, 1946.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And beyond this, he would-- he was only in Auschwitz for a few weeks, and he knew that we were in Lager C.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know what lager-- each lager was separated with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You touched it and you burned up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he managed to find some pieces of wood as they were building these various blocks, they called, the barracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There were some pieces of wood, and he found a knife somehow, and he carved the messages onto these pieces of wood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Kept saying, you must live, you must live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The messages were always the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he would throw it to the next camp, and he would beg people to throw it to the next camp, until it finally will reach the Katz girls.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
